Package: pollr
Title: Data analysis of survey questions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Antoine", "Girard", , "antoine.girard@datag.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to analyze and visualize responses to survey questions. Supports single-choice, multiple-choice and sub-questions formats, with or without weighting. Generate three types of output : a tidy summary table, a styled HTML table and an interactive plot.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    forcats,
    ggplot2,
    ggiraph,
    kableExtra,
    srvyr,
    glue,
    purrr
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
LazyData: true
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
